Step 1. Create helm project -> helm create todolist

configure deployment, values and chart


Testing local
1. minikube start
2. helm install springboot ./springboot-app
3. kubectl get pods

4. minikube ip OR minikube service todolist 

NOTE todolist is the service name we chose in nodeport



NOW AgroCD


1. kubectl create namespace argocd
2. install kubectl apply -n argocd \
  -f https://raw.githubusercontent.com/argoproj/argo-cd/stable/manifests/install.yaml

3. kubectl get pods -n agrocd

4. kubectl port-forward svc/argocd-server -n argocd 8080:443

5. NOW CREATE application.yaml.. one time step to create and apply it

6. kubectl apply -f application.yaml

7. minikube ip... kubectl get svc to check status